<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TKT2">
<l>kāṟṟiṉaip puṉalait tīyaik kaṭimati ḷilaṅkai ceṟṟa</l>
<l>ēṟṟiṉai yimayam mēya veḻilmaṇit tiraḷai yiṉpa</l>
<l>āṟṟiṉai yamutan taṉṉai yavuṇaṉā ruyirai yuṇṭa</l>
<l>kūṟṟiṉaik kuṇaṅkoṇ ṭuḷḷaṅ kūṟunī kūṟu māṟē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Wind, water, [and] fire, the bull which destroyed strong-walled Lanka,</l>
<l>The cluster of lovely jewels which dwelled in the Himalayas, river of delight,</l>
<l>[This] nectar, Death who consumed the dear life of the demon -</l>
<l>Having grasped [his] qualities, [my] heart, tell the way that you tell [about him].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
